&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>So peeps, it’s time for part two of my “Digital Disasters I Survived” series—today’s freak‑out is about ChatGPT. In the name of &lt;em>“context”&lt;/em> and &lt;em>“personal recommendations”&lt;/em>, a bunch of y’all spilled your &lt;em>whole life&lt;/em> to a chatbot thinking it was private. Midnight rants, therapy-style journaling, emotional overshares—it’s like the bot became your digital psychoanalyst.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>